# Same-origin proxy to the Champions Battle Data API so the web app can read the
# per-forme CSV files (which the origin serves without CORS headers). Netlify and
# Cloudflare Pages honor this file; the app falls back to the CORS JSON endpoint
# on hosts that don't (base species only). The status 200 makes it a rewrite/proxy
# rather than a client redirect.
/cbd/*  https://championsbattledata.com/:splat  200
